            "content": "## 🛡️ PHASE 1: Intake & Approval Gating\nTriggers from Salesforce. Fetches ERP/Legal data and determines the approval depth (up to 6 levels). Pauses for manual approval via Webhook Wait nodes before proceeding to document assembly."
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
